  <h2 id="accordion-animation">
    Accordion Animation
    <sup>EXPERIMENTAL</sup>
  </h2>
  <p>
    The accordion features smooth animations with progressive enhancement when
    expanding and collapsing content sections. This is an experimental feature
    that may not be supported in all browsers.
  </p>
  <p>
    The accordion uses modern CSS features like
    <code>interpolate-size: allow-keywords</code>
    that enable smooth transitions for intrinsic size values and
    <code>transition-behavior: allow-discrete</code>
    to allow smoother transitions for discrete properties like
    <code>content-visibility</code>
    .
  </p>
